Class Syphon

  • java.lang.Object
    • codeanticode.syphon.Syphon

  • public class Syphon
extends Object
    Processing library that encapsulates Syphon clients and servers. Syphon is an open source Mac OS X technology that allows applications to share frames - full frame rate video or stills - with one another in realtime. http://syphon.v002.info/
